{tarflow} includes code from other open source projects. The following
is a list of these projects (a full copy of the license agreement
used by these projects is included below):

- Miles McBain's {dflow} package
- Miles McBain's {fnmate} package

The code in the "rstudio-addin.R" and "tar_add_fn.R" files is derived
almost entirely from the {fnmate} package and is licensed to you under
the MIT License, the terms of which are included below. You can obtain
the source code for {fnmate} at:

https://github.com/MilesMcBain/fnmate

The code in the "use_tarflow.R" file is derived heavily from
the {dflow} package and is licensed to you under the MIT License,
the terms of which are included below. You can obtain the source code
for {dflow} at:

https://github.com/MilesMcBain/dflow




